{"tid":786464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"優品360°老闆：阿信屋10億樓下我有興趣","createTime":"2018-08-20T02:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T03:06:34.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2176d208e02707992417484c524d83fb7858fcc0","tid":786464,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180820/large/1534732499_29ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180820%2Flarge%2F1534732499_29ac.jpg&h=507ab728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於759阿信屋創辦人突然離世，作為業務競爭對手的優品360&deg;老闆林子峰向本報表示擔心，因為怕759阿信屋會賣俾一個強者。他不諱言對759阿信屋（即CEC國際（759））有興趣，殼連公司市值約6億元，如果10億元以下都會有興趣，以免被強者崛起打倒自己。<br />\n<br />\n林子峰表示，佢（林偉駿）都唔識做生意，亂咁開舖，開成200幾間。舉例用3萬元租1間舖，租夠5間，先賺150萬元生意，租金佔收入10%。我都係租金佔收入10%，但我15萬元租1間舖做150萬元生意。另外人手及物流控制亦非理想做法。"},{"pid":"b33cb31f4044b5ad7e0979c3b03cd54e1821d478","tid":786464,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:55:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180820/58584596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180820%2F58584596&d=4T8dbDUuPIXk%2FVoA3xnEsTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=3f855e3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180820%2F58584596&h=9deef71f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180820/58584596</a>"},{"pid":"1a6f32248e72d7df911de8dafe40adc95b3bdea9","tid":786464,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:56:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾!"},{"pid":"f3c5f5ab128b936cd970e7396ae310c38c65c55c","tid":786464,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"支那又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class